//
// Cyclostatic acquire on BOTH outer (W) and inner (X) loops with different
// fifos (#2463). Each loop drains its hoisted carry via a trailing release;
// the IRON design in test.py declares both nested loops and the peel rewrite
// keeps both producer-side locks draining instead of deadlocking.
//
// REQUIRES: ryzen_ai_npu2, peano, xrt_python_bindings
//
// RUN: %run_on_npu2% %python %S/test.py
